<cb:div type="nanchuan-notes">
<head>漢譯南傳大藏經 註解</head>
<p>
<note n="0100001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0100001">底本與暹羅本作 pādapaggaṁ 意義不詳，今採用異本脚註之 Padamaggaṁ。</note>
<note n="0103001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0103001">採用暹羅本之 ajaro bhave。</note>
<note n="0106001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0106001">底本為 sakaṭakaṁ 意義不詳，暹羅本為 sakatikaṁ 此亦不見於巴利語辭書，梵語辭書中有 Koṭika 之植物名，今依此，但為何種植物不詳。</note>
<note n="0107001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0107001">「四方」。底本雖有 cātuddīpā，但分採用暹羅本之 catuddisā。</note>
<note n="0109001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109001">採用暹羅本之 na kenaci 'haṁ vijjhāmi。</note>
<note n="0109002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109002">採用暹羅之 kathaṁ sa paridipento aniccaṁ tatthudāhari。</note>
<note n="0110001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110001">「最初為自食」，採用暹羅本之 aggaṁ bhunjjeyam attanā。</note>
<note n="0111002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0111002">「引導至自家」，採用暹羅本之 bhikkhū netvā sahaṁgharaṁ。</note>
<note n="0112003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0112003">「今日我施物……」，採用暹羅本之 ajjāpi deyyadhamo me mamaṁ toseti sabbadā。</note>
<note n="0114001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0114001">「軍中我無缺」，採用暹羅本之 balakāye bhave c' eva。</note>
<note n="0115001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0115001">底本讀為 sovaṇṇ-akattarika，與本文內容不相一致，應讀為 sovaṇṇakuntalikā。</note>
<note n="0115002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0115002">底本為 soṇṇakattaraṁ，依本文之內容應讀 soṇṇakuntalaṁ。</note>
<note n="0116001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0116001"><space quantity="0"/></note>
</p>
